<h2>Individual Awards</h2>

<p>
  Individual ribbons will be awarded to the first, second, and third place
  winner of each category. The judges have sole responsibility for
  determining if all of the ribbons in a particular category should be
  awarded, or if there are ties for a particular ribbon.
</p>

<h2>Best of Show</h2>

<p>
  Best of Show will be awarded from the judging of all first place entries, except
  for ciders and meads. The Best of Show winner will have the opportunity to have
their beer brewed at Linden Street Brewing. Winner will be reponsible for any travel
necessary to get to Linden. Brett and other interestingly fermented beers will not be eligible for this prize.
</p>
